close_reason: Queue pruning implemented via TELEMETRY_MAX_QUEUE_ENTRY_ATTEMPTS=15. Entries with 15+ attempts are automatically dropped during flush. Existing stuck entries will be pruned on next flush cycle.
body: "Current state: 190 entries in events.jsonl, 59 over 1MB, 130MB total. Most entries are in exponential backoff with next_attempt_after far in the future. These will never succeed because the endpoint rejects payloads over ~1MB. Cleanup: remove entries with attempts > 10 or size > 500KB."
